<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 01:02:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国称RTX因向中国和其他国家出口而被罚款2亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rtx-pay-200-million-fine-export-mistakes-state-department-says-2024-08-30/</link><description>美国国务院周四的记录称，RTX Corp 将支付 2 亿美元罚款，以了结有关这家航空航天和国防公司因与包括中国在内的被禁止国家交换数据和产品而违反出口法的指控。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rtx-pay-200-million-fine-export-mistakes-state-department-says-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于房地产行业承压，中国顶级银行第二季度利润下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-banks-post-lower-second-quarter-profit-property-sector-weighs-2024-08-30/</link><description>中国五家最大的银行中有四家本周报告第二季度利润下降，此前政府为了在经济放缓和房地产行业陷入困境的情况下刺激贷款需求而降低贷款利率。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-banks-post-lower-second-quarter-profit-property-sector-weighs-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易代表办公室推迟对中国关税的最终决定，未来几天将发布公告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/ustr-says-decision-section-301-tariffs-chinese-imports-be-announced-coming-days-2024-08-30/</link><description>拜登政府周五再次推迟宣布美国对中国制造的电动汽车、电池、半导体和太阳能电池大幅提高关税的最终决定，并表示将在未来几天内公布决定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:26:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/ustr-says-decision-section-301-tariffs-chinese-imports-be-announced-coming-days-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>西班牙首相桑切斯下月访华，因中欧贸易争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/spains-sanchez-visit-china-next-month-amid-beijing-eu-trade-dispute-2024-08-30/</link><description>西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯办公室周五表示，西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯将于下个月访问中国，以北京对欧盟猪肉进口进行反倾销调查为背景。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 12:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/spains-sanchez-visit-china-next-month-amid-beijing-eu-trade-dispute-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>国务院审议通过数据安全管理条例草案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cabinet-passes-draft-regulations-data-security-management-2024-08-30/</link><description>官方媒体周五称，中国国务院已通过数据安全管理条例草案。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 11:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cabinet-passes-draft-regulations-data-security-management-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国市场监管机构称电子商务巨头阿里巴巴已完成三年“整顿”期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-market-regulator-says-e-commerce-giant-alibaba-has-completed-three-year-2024-08-30/</link><description>中国国家市场监管总局周五发表声明称，阿里巴巴集团继2021年因垄断行为被处以罚款后，已完成三年“整改”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:59:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-market-regulator-says-e-commerce-giant-alibaba-has-completed-three-year-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>台军方称中国缺乏入侵能力，但还有其他选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ministry-says-china-lacks-ability-invade-has-other-options-2024-08-30/</link><description>台湾国防部表示，中国缺乏“全面”入侵台湾的能力，因为它没有装备，但正在引进先进的新武器，并有其他选择来威胁台湾，例如检查外国货船。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 08:13:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ministry-says-china-lacks-ability-invade-has-other-options-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国监管机构称特斯拉北京将召回870辆进口Model X电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-beijing-recall-870-imported-model-x-evs-china-regulator-says-2024-08-30/</link><description>用于连接屋顶的粘合剂可能会造成安全隐患。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 07:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-beijing-recall-870-imported-model-x-evs-china-regulator-says-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于国际旅行缓慢，中国顶级航空公司出现亏损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-top-airlines-post-losses-hit-by-slow-international-travel-domestic-2024-08-30/</link><description>中国主要国有航空公司上半年出现亏损，原因是国际旅行反弹慢于预期、国内供应过剩以及全球航空运力恢复带来的竞争更加激烈。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 07:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-top-airlines-post-losses-hit-by-slow-international-travel-domestic-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国国有银行在人民币快速升值的情况下买入美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-state-banks-buying-dollars-amid-rapid-yuan-gains-sources-say-2024-08-30/</link><description>四名知情人士表示，主要国有银行周五在中国在岸外汇市场买入美元，以减缓人民币升值。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 06:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-state-banks-buying-dollars-amid-rapid-yuan-gains-sources-say-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国2024年、2025年房价前景恶化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-home-price-outlook-2024-2025-worsens-2024-08-30/</link><description>路透调查显示，中国房价今年和明年的下跌速度将快于此前预测，因为北京的支持政策难以帮助房地产行业触底。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 06:40:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-home-price-outlook-2024-2025-worsens-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与越南在南海紧张局势中加强军事关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-sign-defence-agreement-2024-08-30/</link><description>越南和菲律宾周五同意推进防务和军事关系，并深化海上安全合作，这是两国在南海行动上长期存在分歧的重要一步。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 06:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-sign-defence-agreement-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>8月份中国工厂活动继续下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-seen-extending-declines-aug-2024-08-30/</link><description>路透社周五的一项民意调查显示，中国八月份的工厂活动可能连续第四个月萎缩，这强化了官员对家庭采取更多刺激措施、减少建设项目刺激措施的必要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 05:56:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-seen-extending-declines-aug-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>独家：俄罗斯与中国合作伙伴的付款障碍八月份加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russia-payment-hurdles-with-china-partners-intensified-august-sources-say-2024-08-30/</link><description>价值数百亿元的交易陷入僵局。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 05:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russia-payment-hurdles-with-china-partners-intensified-august-sources-say-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾关于萨宾娜浅滩损害的说法没有科学事实依据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-publishes-first-survey-report-disputed-south-china-seas-sabina-shoal-2024-08-30/</link><description>中国周五发布了对南海有争议的萨比纳浅滩的第一份调查报告，称菲律宾提出的珊瑚礁破坏主张没有科学或事实依据。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 02:29:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-publishes-first-survey-report-disputed-south-china-seas-sabina-shoal-2024-08-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>